[ Upstream commit 0591183699fceeafb4c4141072d47775de83ecfb ]

[Why]
Reported from customer the checksum in AMD VSIF V3 is incorrect and
causing blank screen issue.

[How]
Fix the packet length issue on AMD HDMI VSIF V3.

